ost in Ghent from early 2017, in the role as Revenue and Reservations Manager, and just recently departed to look for new challenges overseas.  Prior to The Post I had the pleasure of working with Nicolas at Phum Baitang Resort in Cambodia, were he was assisting our Reservations department, in key aspects of revenue management. Nicolas was a very well organized, showed good leadership skills, nice can do attitude and is very well liked amongst his teams. I would have no hesitation in recommending Nicolas to my colleagues in the industry, and certainly hope we have the opportunity to work together in the near future.  ", "recommendations/0/name": "Nicolas Le Guellaut", "recommendations/0/subtitle": "Manager at Finca Serrato", "recommendations/0/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/nicolas-le-guellaut-a1522a94/", "recommendations/0/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABP3gzEB7b45irlqckfrA-bpiRzjgdObtdY", "recommendations/1/date": "January 16, 2019", "recommendations/1/description": "Zelie, worked with Zannier Hotels on our first major project in Europe, called 1898 The Post in Ghent from early 2017, in the role as Resident Manager, and just recently departed to look for new challenges overseas.  Prior to The Post, I had the pleasure of working with Zelie at Phum Baitang Resort in Cambodia, were she managing our front office team. Zelie was very well organized and a very competent Manager, she showed excellent leadership skills, a can do attitude at all times, combined with a good spirit around her teams. I would have no hesitation in recommending Zelie to my colleagues in the industry, and certainly hope we have the opportunity to work together in the near future.", "recommendations/1/name": "Zélie Paulin", "recommendations/1/subtitle": "Manager at Finca Serrato", "recommendations/1/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/zélie-paulin-a549b7b2/", "recommendations/1/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABf_PCABGROpqo0zDTHLRbqxp5wqDTUn2aM", "recommendations/2/context": "David was Allan Gus